sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as "Local browser/test client"
    participant App as "BlogAI.Web Blazor app"
    participant Home as "Route: /"
    participant LocalDev as "Route: /local-dev"
    participant Auth as "Auth/API dependency"

    Note over App: Local/dev shell only
    Client->>App: GET /
    App->>Home: Render presentation-only home page
    Home-->>App: BlogAI shell content
    App-->>Client: 200 OK

    Client->>App: GET /local-dev
    App->>LocalDev: Render service-boundary placeholder
    LocalDev-->>App: Placeholder content
    App-->>Client: 200 OK

    Note over App,Auth: No auth UI, production auth, service call, persistence, localization resources, deployment config, or BlogEngine.NET dependency in this slice
